WEBVTT

00:02.000 --> 00:29.025
Subtitles byMemoryOnSmells
http://UKsubtitles.ru.

00:33.861 --> 00:36.844
'Though we were only
in our early 20s,

00:36.845 --> 00:37.887
'a little more than girls,

00:37.888 --> 00:41.869
'we served the women of the East End
in their hour of greatest need.'

00:42.869 --> 00:44.860
'In return for our care,

00:44.861 --> 00:48.852
'they gave us the most precious
gift they could...

00:48.853 --> 00:50.860
'their trust.

00:50.861 --> 00:53.800
'This made us brave and tireless.

00:53.801 --> 00:56.880
'And in the main,
we did not doubt ourselves

00:56.881 --> 00:58.869
'because we were not doubted.'

01:00.809 --> 01:02.892
'But we were not invincible.

01:02.893 --> 01:06.873
'There were times when we faced
challenges and choices of our own.'

01:08.000 --> 01:14.074
